txt.en: 'Meow! Welcome back. I think that last quest took a lot out of you, but you don't look too worse for the wear. Too bad the same can't be said for your equipment!\n\nAnyway, it looks like you want to complete Book X now. That whole business with Mordrambor is interesting, isn't it? Well, I thought so at least, you'll be skipping over all that, so you won't get a chance to read it.
Completion of this quest will flag your character has having completed all the quests in Book X of the Epic quest series.
